          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-0ea4c8452c7ef96f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Sign up for BMO Online Banking\nRegister for BMO Online Banking and start using the BMO mobile banking app.\nSavings Amplifier Account FAQs\nWhat is a savings account?\nA savings account is a deposit account designed to hold money you don\u2019t plan to\nspend right away. It\u2019s different from a chequing account, as you usually do not\nwithdrawal money from a savings account on an everyday basis.\nA savings account is ideal if you\u2019re trying to set money aside for a big purchase or\nfinancial move, such as a vacation, a car purchase, buying property, or completing a\nhome renovation. With BMO Savings Goals, we can help you set, track, and manage\nyour savings to reach your financial goals. Customers with a BMO savings account\ncan access the BMO Savings goals feature for no fee.\nWhat is a high-interest savings account (HISA)?\nWhat is a Premium Rate Savings Account?\nCan I open a Savings Builder Account",
